        <updateDate>2019-12-13T23:01:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Internet Exchange Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill creates a grant program for the establishment and expansion of facilities through which internet service providers and content delivery networks exchange internet traffic (internet exchange facilities) in unserved or underserved areas.</p> <p>Further, the bill allows recipients of funding from the E-Rate and Telehealth programs to apply such funds to the procurement or maintenance of a connection to an internet exchange facility. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
